    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The eternal God entered and stepped into time;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For this He needed persons to carry the line —"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Those who fulfilled His plan, to bring God into man"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Bringing divinity into humanity."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In the universe this is the greatest event,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That is Christ’s incarnation — in His first advent."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Ruth became an ancestor in this mystery —"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God and man to be mingled as one entity."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God had promised the seed of a woman for man"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That would crush Satan’s head and redeem fallen man;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To make God and man one, what a glory to Him!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We are qualified now to partake of Him."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We are Moabites too, constituted with sin;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We are under God’s wrath and His condemnation."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But through Christ’s redemption, He’s our portion we claim;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In this organic union, we’re married to Him."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    }
